{"tid":2292772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得無希望好頹嘅人同我入嚟！","createTime":"2020-11-19T18:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T18:08:18.000Z","uid":297843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48f8a0563b948a86526f5fac606f964aeed6aaf0","tid":2292772,"uid":297843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"我而家同你哋講！<br />\n我哋有一日會贏㗎！<br />\n記唔記得二百萬人遊行？<br />\n記唔記得7月1號齊上齊落？<br />\n記唔記得每一個你遇到嘅手足？<br />\n手足犧牲好多嘢，係好心痛好絕望，<br />\n但唔好唔記得點解當初一齊行出嚟！<br />\n嗌住同一句號！<br />\n<br />\n因為我哋相信世界會因為我哋變得更好！<br />\n因為我哋想好人有好人報！<br />\n無論世界而家幾差，幾無力都好！<br />\n最起碼做到嘅嘢，就係唔會俾佢哋同化，<br />\n記住一點一滴，記得點解最初要行出去，唔好頹！<br />\n好好做人！<br />\n只要有信念，總有一日可以推倒高牆。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">唔知你哋信唔信，但我好撚信！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2zx-wdO0L20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2zx-wdO0L20&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=1eae70d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2zx-wdO0L20</a>"},{"pid":"e7d526a3e9432ce2f92d94b2d929641ae98e5a55","tid":2292772,"uid":297843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"3d864532e32691583c575bf2d2abfee91b9e3a1e","tid":2292772,"uid":297843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T18:08:18.000Z","msg":"Up"}]}